> You are only allowed to have five 
  spawners of any type running at any 
  given time. Except for villager spawners, 
  which are banned.

> Spawners systems must pick up all drops/xp 
  and kill all the mobs quickly after spawning.

> You may only have 20 lava generators running 
  in your base at a time per person.

> Your RFTool dimensions must be set to private 
  and shared ONLY with your team mates.

> Spread out your machines, and don't make 
  excessive lag. Anchors load 3x3 chunks.

> Do not use anti-afk machines.

> Don't use more than 1 Dimension Builder.

> No weather/time control (Witchery, etc...).